Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensory hacks that actually work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep noise-canceling headphones\Nin your bag at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without music, they cut\Noverwhelming sounds by 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Game changer for grocery stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let your kid wear sunglasses indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluorescent lights are brutal\Nfor sensory-sensitive kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what people think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rotate fidgets weekly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids get bored. The novelty\Nis what keeps them working.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Number four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chewing is calming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chew necklaces, crunchy snacks,\Nthick smoothies through a straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Offer them before the meltdown starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Save this for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow for more autism parenting tips.
